I don't want any calls.

228
00:15:49,633 --> 00:15:51,586
Nope. None at all.

229
00:16:01,415 --> 00:16:02,915
<i>Hello?</i>

230
00:16:05,894 --> 00:16:07,691
<i>It's Burt, from the front desk.</i>

231
00:16:10,586 --> 00:16:12,959
