for not believing Sammy.

247
00:17:46,898 --> 00:17:48,398
You know the truth about my condition, Officer?

248
00:17:49,819 --> 00:17:51,319
You don't know anything.

249
00:17:51,789 --> 00:17:53,289
You feel angry. You don't know why.

250
00:17:54,039 --> 00:17:56,849
You feel guilty...
You have no idea why.

251
00:17:57,847 --> 00:18:00,537
