You <i>are</i> a fuckin' cop...

349
00:28:48,872 --> 00:28:51,897
Yeah! And I'm the guy
that helped you find him!

350
00:28:51,922 --> 00:28:53,489
Get up! Get up!

351
00:28:54,203 --> 00:28:56,206
Lenny, you got the wrong idea!

352
00:28:59,060 --> 00:29:00,794
