- No. Yeah, that and your thing.

359
00:29:20,249 --> 00:29:24,222
Look! Leonard, Jimmy's your guy.
I just figured we'd make a few dollars on the side!

360
00:29:24,247 --> 00:29:26,413
- How did he know me?
- The Discount Inn.

361
00:29:26,875 --> 00:29:28,030
 He dealt out of there.

362
00:29:28,054 --> 00:29:30,883
