taking a picture of the dump!

364
00:29:34,070 --> 00:29:36,290
- You're fucking using me.
- No! You get half!

365
00:29:36,315 --> 00:29:39,189
He knew about Sammy! Why would I
tell him about fuckin' Sammy?!

366
00:29:39,214 --> 00:29:42,214
You tell everybody about Sammy!
-Everybody who'll listen!

367
00:29:42,477 --> 00:29:44,320
<i>"Remember Sammy Jankis?"
"Remember Sammy Jankis?"</i>

368
00:29:44,948 --> 00:29:47,792
Great story.
Gets better every time you tell it.

369
00:29:48,812 --> 00:29:50,363
So you lie to yourself to be happy.

370
00:29:50,388 --> 00:29:52,898
There's nothing wrong with that!
We all do it.

371
00:29:52,923 --> 00:29:55,767
Who cares if there's a few little details
you'd rather not remember?

372
00:29:58,519 --> 00:29:59,738
What the fuck are you talking about?

373
00:29:59,762 --> 00:30:01,262
