anguish tearing her up inside.

377
00:30:10,805 --> 00:30:12,305
The "insulin".

378
00:30:13,423 --> 00:30:14,950
That's Sammy, not me.

379
00:30:15,112 --> 00:30:16,246
I told you about Sammy.

380
00:30:16,270 --> 00:30:19,251
Yeah, right.
Like you tell yourself over and over again.

381
00:30:19,453 --> 00:30:21,367
"Conditioning" yourself to remember.

382
00:30:21,392 --> 00:30:24,249
- Learning through repetition.
- Sammy let his wife kill herself.

383
00:30:24,274 --> 00:30:25,687
Sammy ended up in an institution..

384
00:30:25,711 --> 00:30:27,473
Sammy was a con-man.

385
00:30:27,498 --> 00:30:28,998
-A faker.

386
00:30:29,886 --> 00:30:31,386
