<i>-A fraud.</i>

388
00:30:34,782 --> 00:30:36,445
And I was wrong...
That's the whole point!

389
00:30:38,093 --> 00:30:40,778
- See, Sammy's wife came to me.
- Sammy didn't have a wife!

390
00:30:43,938 --> 00:30:45,701
