391
00:30:52,947 --> 00:30:54,447
Ouch!

392
00:30:56,345 --> 00:30:57,845
My wife wasn't diabetic.

393
00:30:58,689 --> 00:31:00,189
You sure?

394
00:31:05,103 --> 00:31:07,626
- Ouch. <i>Cut it out.</i>
- She wasn't diabetic!

395
00:31:09,181 --> 00:31:10,821
You think I don't know my own wife?

396
00:31:11,495 --> 00:31:12,468
What the fuck is wrong with you?

397
00:31:12,492 --> 00:31:16,295
Well, I guess I can only make you remember
the things you wanna be true.

398
00:31:16,611 --> 00:31:18,775
- Like old Jimmy down there.
- He's not the right guy.

399
00:31:19,017 --> 00:31:20,517
