whether he was your guy or not?

402
00:31:27,658 --> 00:31:29,991
- It makes <i>all</i> the difference.
- Why? You're never gonna know.

403
00:31:30,016 --> 00:31:30,767
- Yes, I will.
- No, you won't.

404
00:31:30,791 --> 00:31:32,752
I will. Somehow I'll know.

405
00:31:32,777 --> 00:31:35,004
- You won't remember!
- When it's done, I will know. It'll be different.

406
00:31:35,029 --> 00:31:38,775
