412
00:31:50,562 --> 00:31:52,062
Look, Lenny.

413
00:31:52,556 --> 00:31:54,552
I was the cop assigned to your wife's case.

414
00:31:54,577 --> 00:31:55,384
-I believed you.

415
00:31:55,408 --> 00:31:57,623
