419
00:32:08,196 --> 00:32:09,811
But you didn't remember.

420
00:32:10,749 --> 00:32:12,249
So I helped you...

421
00:32:12,416 --> 00:32:13,509
start looking again...

422
00:32:13,533 --> 00:32:15,533
